com.helger.jcodemodel.writer

Class JFormatter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.helger.jcodemodel.writer.JFormatter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IJFormatter, Closeable, AutoCloseable

    @NotThreadSafe
public class JFormatter
extends Object
implements IJFormatter
    This is a utility class for managing indentation and other basic formatting for PrintWriter.
